Term Project Topic:
The above definitions can be
refined so that they are mathematically precise.
You can then implement a consistency checker based
upon these precise definitions,
and apply your consistency checker on an
example such as the Product & Servicer Customization
System presented in previous slides.
This topic is for those who are mathematically inclined.
